nodes.text: Ihouse was an establishment located in a seedy part of the Coruscant Underworld. It was situated next to Purple Werm, and across the street from Sleeping Rose. A luminous Aurebesh sign stated the name of the establishment.
During the Clone Wars, bounty hunter Cad Bane stayed in an apartment opposite Ihouse, while planning a mission to break into the Jedi Temple.
During pre-production, Ihouse was known as "Gala".
